examples.en: The poker glowed red-hot in the fire.
Poker is a game of chance.
I'm game for a little poker.
Veteran poker players invariably have expressionless faces, regardless of the hand they're holding.
He plays a mean game of poker.
He plays poker most every evening.
Poker is a game of luck and skill.
My uncle likes to kibitz when I play poker with my cousins.
He would often gamble hundreds of dollars on a hand of poker.
He kept a resolutely inexpressive face throughout the poker game.
